            "en": "<p>You must pay the one-off fee for the application for recognition as an SR expert.</p><ul><li>For <strong>2023</strong>, the one-off fee is <strong>681 </strong>euros.</li><li>The one-off fee is index-adjusted every year.</li></ul><p>As a recognised SR expert, you must pay the <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\">annual fee</a> for the supervision of the recognition. You will receive an invoice for this by post at the start of the calendar year in your name at your official address.</p><ul><li>For <strong>2023 </strong>the annual fee amounts to <strong>136</strong> euros.</li></ul>",
